Greek Debt Swap Writedown Probably to Top 21%, French Aide Says

-- B y   M a r k   D e e n
-- 
2011-10-13T09:49:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-13/greek-debt-swap-writedown-probably-to-top-21-french-aide-says.html
Greek bondholders will probably have
to take losses deeper than the 21 percent foreseen in a debt
swap that was part of a July 21 bailout agreement, a French
official told reporters today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
